<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.10.3">
<l>umpa rulakēḻu kaṭalēḻu malaiyēḻu moḻiyāmai muṉanāḷ</l>
<l>tampoṉ vayiṟāra ḷavumuṇṭa vaiyumiḻnta taṭamārvar takaicēr</l>
<l>vampu malarkiṉṟa poḻilpaimpoṉ varutumpi maṇikaṅkul vayalcūḻ</l>
<l>nampa ṉuṟaikiṉṟa nakarnanti puraviṇṇa karamnaṇṇu maṉamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O heart, go to Nantipura Viṇṇakaram</l>
<l rend="indent">encircled by dark jewel[-like] paddy fields</l>
<l>Where dragonflies, [like] green gold, come to the groves</l>
<l rend="indent">where fragrances spread,</l>
<l>The city where dwells the merciful lord, the one with a broad chest who,</l>
<l rend="indent">having long ago eaten the seven heavenly worlds, seven seas,</l>
<l rend="indent">and seven mountains,</l>
<l>To the full extent of his golden stomach, without leaving [anything],</l>
<l rend="indent">disgorged them.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
